title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Paradoxically, you could get more bang for your buck from a pleasurable endeavor by spending less today. It might sound counterintuitive to be economical with quality, but sometimes a similar product and service can be as good, if not better, on a budget. For instance, you probably dont need the fanciest gym in the city for reestablishing your exercise regimen when one in close proximity is actually a smarter option. Start off practical and small, then build up with consistency and perseverance. A modest beginning can lead to majestic results when youre the key ingredient to it all.
